---
permalink: "/onepage.html"
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
noindex: true
title: "G Flexipack — Flexible Packaging Manufacturer · Bharuch, India"
description: "Custom-printed flexible packaging from Bharuch, Gujarat. Thirteen pouch formats, 8-colour rotogravure print, ISO 9001:2015, 300+ MT/month capacity, MOQ 5,000."
pageImage: "/assets/images/standup.png"
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
{% include "partials/head.njk" %}
  <style>
{{ "src/assets/css/styles.css" | inlineFile | safe }}
  </style>
</head>
<body id="top">

  <!-- ============ NAV (in-page anchors) ============ -->
  <header class="nav">
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a class="brand" href="#top" aria-label="G Flexipack, home">
        <img src="/assets/images/logo.png" alt="G Flexipack" />
      </a>
      <nav class="nav-links" aria-label="Primary">
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#products">Products</a>
        <a href="#industries">Industries</a>
        <a href="#quality">Quality</a>
        <a href="#infrastructure">Infrastructure</a>
      </nav>
      <a class="nav-cta" href="#inquiry">
        Get a quote <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-progress" id="navProgress" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  </header>

  <!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
  <section class="hh-hero" id="hero">
    <div class="hh-hero-inner">
      <div class="hh-hero-text">
        <p class="hh-eyebrow">Flexible packaging · Est. {{ site.founded }}</p>
        <h1 class="hh-hero-title">Packaging built for <em>shelf impact.</em></h1>
        <p class="hh-hero-sub">
          G Flexipack is a flexible packaging manufacturer in Bharuch, Gujarat — custom-printed pouches
          for food, beverage and lifestyle brands. Thirteen formats, printed, laminated and converted under one roof.
        </p>
        <div class="hh-hero-ctas">
          <a class="cta cta-primary" href="#inquiry">Get a quote <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
          <a class="cta hh-cta-ghost" href="#infrastructure">See the plant <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hh-marquee" aria-label="Formats we print and sectors we pack for">
        <div class="hh-col">
          <div class="hh-track hh-down">
            {% for p in products %}<article class="hh-tile" style="--bg:#3b2a20; --bandc:#eae0cd; --band-text:#3b2a20;"><img class="hh-photo" src="/assets/images/{{ p.image }}.png" alt="{{ p.name }}" loading="lazy" /><span class="hh-tag">{{ p.short }}</span></article>
            {% endfor %}{% for p in products %}<article class="hh-tile" style="--bg:#3b2a20; --bandc:#eae0cd; --band-text:#3b2a20;"><img class="hh-photo" src="/assets/images/{{ p.image }}.png" alt="{{ p.name }}" loading="lazy" /><span class="hh-tag">{{ p.short }}</span></article>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hh-col">
          <div class="hh-track hh-up">
            {% for s in industries %}<article class="hh-tile" style="--bg:{{ s.accent }}; --bandc:#3b2a20; --band-text:#eae0cd;"><img class="hh-photo" src="/assets/images/{{ s.image }}.png" alt="{{ s.short }} sector packaging" loading="lazy" /><span class="hh-tag">{{ s.short }}</span></article>
            {% endfor %}{% for s in industries %}<article class="hh-tile" style="--bg:{{ s.accent }}; --bandc:#3b2a20; --band-text:#eae0cd;"><img class="hh-photo" src="/assets/images/{{ s.image }}.png" alt="{{ s.short }} sector packaging" loading="lazy" /><span class="hh-tag">{{ s.short }}</span></article>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="hh-meta" aria-label="At a glance">
    <div><strong>Thirteen <em>formats</em>.</strong> Stand-up, zipper, gusseted, spout, retort and more — all printed to spec, in-house.</div>
    <div><strong>From <em>{{ site.moq }}</em>.</strong> One of the lowest rotogravure MOQs in the market — trial orders welcome.</div>
    <div><strong>Quote in <em>{{ site.quoteTurnaround }}</em>.</strong> Send artwork, size, quantity and target ship-by date. We come back the next business day.</div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ WELCOME ============ -->
  <section class="sec welcome" id="about">
    <div class="sec-head" data-reveal>
      <p class="sec-eyebrow">Welcome to our company</p>
      <h2 class="sec-title">Quality packaging, <em>since {{ site.founded }}.</em></h2>
      <p class="sec-lead">
        G Flexipack is a flexible packaging manufacturer in Bharuch, Gujarat, built on the
        {{ site.group }}'s 20+ years of manufacturing heritage. We print, laminate, slit and
        convert custom pouches for brands across food, pharma, personal care and industry —
        in a climate-controlled, dust-free plant designed to international hygiene standards.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ VISION & MISSION ============ -->
  <section class="sec vm" aria-label="Vision and mission">
    <div class="vm-grid">
      <div class="vm-panel" style="--vc:#b25c2e;" data-reveal>
        <span class="vm-label">Our Vision</span>
        <p class="vm-quote">To be the flexible packaging <em>partner of choice</em> for brands that care how their product lands on shelf.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="vm-panel" style="--vc:#7a6e3f;" data-reveal>
        <span class="vm-label">Our Mission</span>
        <p class="vm-quote">Design and print custom pouches that <em>protect the product</em> and represent the brand.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ TICKER ============ -->
  <div class="ticker" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="ticker-track">
      {% for i in [1, 2] %}<div class="ticker-set">
        <span class="ticker-item"><em>8-colour</em> rotogravure</span><span class="ticker-star">✻</span>
        <span class="ticker-item">Food-grade <em>barrier films</em></span><span class="ticker-star">✻</span>
        <span class="ticker-item">ISO <em>9001:2015</em></span><span class="ticker-star">✻</span>
        <span class="ticker-item"><em>300+ MT</em> a month</span><span class="ticker-star">✻</span>
        <span class="ticker-item">Solvent-less <em>lamination</em></span><span class="ticker-star">✻</span>
        <span class="ticker-item"><em>8,000 sq ft</em> climate-controlled plant</span><span class="ticker-star">✻</span>
        <span class="ticker-item">Exporting from <em>Mundra Port</em></span><span class="ticker-star">✻</span>
      </div>{% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ============ PRODUCTS (all 13, inline) ============ -->
  <section id="products">
    <div class="sec" style="padding-bottom:30px;">
      <div class="sec-head" data-reveal>
        <p class="sec-eyebrow">Our products</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title">Thirteen formats, <em>printed to spec.</em></h2>
        <p class="sec-lead">Custom dimensions, laminate structures, barrier levels and full-colour rotogravure print — all produced in-house.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pp-grid">
        {% for p in products %}<a class="pp-card" href="/products/{{ p.slug }}/" data-reveal>
          <span class="pp-card-fig" style="--tbg:{{ p.tbg }};"><img src="/assets/images/{{ p.image }}.png" alt="{{ p.name }}" loading="lazy" /></span>
          <span class="pp-card-body">
            <h3>{{ p.name }}</h3>
            <p>{{ p.applications | join(' · ') }}.</p>
            <span class="pp-card-link">View details →</span>
          </span>
        </a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ INDUSTRIES (all 7, accordion) ============ -->
  <section class="industries" id="industries">
    <div class="sec">
      <div class="sec-head" data-reveal>
        <p class="sec-eyebrow">Industries we serve</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title">Seven sectors, <em>one standard.</em></h2>
        <p class="sec-lead">The hygiene, barrier and documentation adapt to the sector. The print quality doesn't.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="acc" id="indAcc" data-reveal>
        {% for s in industries %}<div class="acc-panel{% if loop.first %} is-open{% endif %}" style="--ic:{{ s.accent }};">
          <img class="acc-photo" src="/assets/images/{{ s.image }}.png" alt="{{ s.name }} sector packaging" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="acc-photo-scrim"></div>
          <div class="acc-closed"><span class="acc-num">{{ s.num }}</span><span class="acc-name-v">{{ s.short }}</span></div>
          <div class="acc-open"><span class="acc-num">{{ s.num }}</span><h3>{{ s.name }}</h3><p>{{ s.applications | join(' · ') }}.</p><a class="r-link" href="/industries/{{ s.slug }}/">Explore sector →</a></div>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      <p class="shelf-hint hint-desktop">Hover a sector to open it</p>
      <p class="shelf-hint hint-mobile">Tap a sector to open it</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ INFRASTRUCTURE ============ -->
  <section class="sec" id="infrastructure">
    <div class="sec-head" data-reveal>
      <p class="sec-eyebrow">Infrastructure</p>
      <h2 class="sec-title">8,000 sq ft in <em>Bharuch, Gujarat.</em></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="scrolly">
      <div class="scrolly-sticky">
        <div class="sc-stage" id="scStage">
          <figure class="sc-shot is-active" data-shot="1" style="margin:0;"><img src="/assets/images/printing-machine.png" alt="8-colour rotogravure printing press" /><figcaption>8-colour rotogravure</figcaption></figure>
          <figure class="sc-shot" data-shot="2" style="margin:0;"><img src="/assets/images/lami.png" alt="Solvent-less lamination machine" /><figcaption>Solvent-less lamination</figcaption></figure>
          <figure class="sc-shot" data-shot="3" style="margin:0;"><img src="/assets/images/slitting-machine.png" alt="Slitting machine" /><figcaption>Slitting line</figcaption></figure>
          <figure class="sc-shot" data-shot="4" style="margin:0;"><img src="/assets/images/pouch.png" alt="Pouching line" /><figcaption>Pouching machines</figcaption></figure>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="scrolly-steps">
        <div class="sc-step is-active" data-step="1">
          <figure class="sc-inline" style="margin:0;"><img src="/assets/images/printing-machine.png" alt="8-colour rotogravure printing press" loading="lazy" /></figure>
          <p class="sc-num">i</p><h3>8-Colour Rotogravure Press</h3>
          <p>Auto registration and web guiding for precise multi-colour print — deep, repeatable colour across long runs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sc-step" data-step="2">
          <figure class="sc-inline" style="margin:0;"><img src="/assets/images/lami.png" alt="Solvent-less lamination machine" loading="lazy" /></figure>
          <p class="sc-num">ii</p><h3>Solvent-Less &amp; Solvent-Based Lamination</h3>
          <p>Food-safe multi-layer bonding and specialised barrier structures, matched to the product inside.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sc-step" data-step="3">
          <figure class="sc-inline" style="margin:0;"><img src="/assets/images/slitting-machine.png" alt="Slitting machine" loading="lazy" /></figure>
          <p class="sc-num">iii</p><h3>Precision Slitting Lines</h3>
          <p>Tension-controlled winding to exact reel widths, ready for downstream pouching or delivery as film rolls.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sc-step" data-step="4">
          <figure class="sc-inline" style="margin:0;"><img src="/assets/images/pouch.png" alt="Pouching line" loading="lazy" /></figure>
          <p class="sc-num">iv</p><h3>Centre- &amp; Side-Seal Pouching</h3>
          <p>Finished pouches converted in-house — every format from stand-up to spout, sealed and inspected on line.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ QUALITY (certs + lab + anatomy) ============ -->
  <section id="quality">
    <div class="sec" style="padding-bottom:20px;">
      <div class="sec-head" data-reveal>
        <p class="sec-eyebrow">Certification</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title">Audited, tested, <em>documented.</em></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="cert-row" data-reveal>
        <div class="cert-emblem"><span class="cert-mark">✦</span><h4>ISO 9001:2015</h4><p>Certified quality management system across procurement, production and dispatch.</p></div>
        <div class="cert-emblem"><span class="cert-mark">✦</span><h4>ASTM Standard QC</h4><p>Eight-test laboratory verification on every batch — GSM to heat-seal strength.</p></div>
        <div class="cert-emblem"><span class="cert-mark">✦</span><h4>100% Recyclable Options</h4><p>Mono-material structures available for EPR-compliant, sustainability-first brands.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    {% include "partials/lab.njk" %}
    {% include "partials/anatomy.njk" %}
  </section>

  <!-- ============ WHY US ============ -->
  <section class="sec" id="why-us">
    <div class="sec-head" data-reveal>
      <p class="sec-eyebrow">Why us</p>
      <h2 class="sec-title">What sets us <em>apart.</em></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="why-grid stagger" data-reveal>
      <div class="why-card" style="--wc:#b25c2e;"><span class="why-glyph">i</span><h4>Assured Quality</h4><p>ISO 9001:2015 systems and an in-house ASTM lab — eight tests on every batch, full documentation at dispatch.</p></div>
      <div class="why-card" style="--wc:#c89a3a;"><span class="why-glyph">ii</span><h4>On-Time Delivery</h4><p>3–5 week production lead times, honestly quoted and tracked — with sea freight coordinated from Mundra Port.</p></div>
      <div class="why-card" style="--wc:#7a6e3f;"><span class="why-glyph">iii</span><h4>Customized Solutions</h4><p>Structure, size, barrier and finish engineered per product — recommendation within 24 hours of your brief.</p></div>
      <div class="why-card" style="--wc:#7a8a6c;"><span class="why-glyph">iv</span><h4>Advanced Machinery</h4><p>8-colour rotogravure with auto registration, solvent-less lamination, precision slitting and pouching lines.</p></div>
      <div class="why-card" style="--wc:#3b2a20;"><span class="why-glyph">v</span><h4>Skilled Workforce</h4><p>An experienced production and QC team under the Gangamani group's 20+ years of manufacturing discipline.</p></div>
      <div class="why-card" style="--wc:#b25c2e;"><span class="why-glyph">vi</span><h4>100% Recyclable Options</h4><p>Mono-material LLDPE structures for EPR-compliant brands — sustainability without sacrificing shelf appeal.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ CLIENTELE ============ -->
  <section class="clientele" aria-label="Our clientele">
    <div class="sec">
      <div class="sec-head" data-reveal>
        <p class="sec-eyebrow">Our clientele</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title">Trusted across sectors <em>and borders.</em></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="client-marquee" data-reveal>
        <div class="client-track">
          {% for i in [1, 2] %}<div class="client-set"{% if i == 2 %} aria-hidden="true"{% endif %}>
            <span class="client-badge"><b>Leading snack brand</b><span>Gujarat · India</span></span>
            <span class="client-badge"><b>Tea exporter</b><span>United Kingdom</span></span>
            <span class="client-badge"><b>Pharma packer</b><span>Maharashtra · India</span></span>
            <span class="client-badge"><b>Spice house</b><span>UAE</span></span>
            <span class="client-badge"><b>Agro seeds brand</b><span>Madhya Pradesh</span></span>
            <span class="client-badge"><b>FMCG group</b><span>East Africa</span></span>
            <span class="client-badge"><b>Dry fruits brand</b><span>Rajasthan · India</span></span>
            <span class="client-badge"><b>Personal care label</b><span>Gujarat · India</span></span>
          </div>{% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="client-note">Client identities protected under supply agreements — references available on request.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {% include "partials/inquiry-form.njk" %}

  {% include "partials/footer.njk" %}

  <script>
{{ "src/assets/js/main.js" | inlineFile | safe }}
  </script>
</body>
</html>
